data.description: Discover your dream home in the heart of Raleigh with BRAND NEW ROOF, gutters, windows, and more! This 5-bedroom, 3-bath haven offers versatility and space. Two secondary bedrooms in the finished basement provide endless possibilities, while a spacious living area and full bath make it perfect for guests, a home office, or an entertainment hub. Sitting on nearly 3/4 acres, this property boasts a 1-car garage, an attached carport for convenience, and a fenced yard for privacy and pet lovers. Don't miss the chance to make this remarkable property your own!
